snippet.title: NES Longplay [379] Super Robin Hood (Unlicensed) (with ending)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Stoneworld

This is super robin hood for the NES, an unlicensed game made by Camerica. The game is good but hard has hell as you can see. This time, the ladder appeared, thanks to snakeeater who give me the solution !

Hope you enjoy. -
